~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~pattern matching operator:

->like
    syntax:
        select *from <tablename> where name like "%a%";

        e.g.
        select*from student where name like "%a%";
        {ye jis bhi name mai (a) ata hoga vo sabhi dikhaye ga}

->select*from student where name like "%u%";
