                                                                GROUP BY:
-----------------------------------------------------------------------

-> group by ro wise which contain common column value to use concept of group by we have to use aggregate function


    count(*)  //no oorecord
    -> sum : for total
    -> max : for maximum value
    -> min : for minimum value
    -> avg : for average value

    syntax:
        select <columnname>,count(*) from  <tablename> group by <columnname>;

        e.g.
            ->select city,count(*) from student group by city;
+-----------+----------+
| city      | count(*) |
+-----------+----------+
| AHMEDABAD |        3 |
| surat     |        2 |
| mumbai    |        1 |
+-----------+----------+

