where and having columns

  where:
  -> apply condition before group

  having:
  -> apply condition after group condition

  having syntax:
        select columnname,count(*),total from <tablename> group by <columnname> having <column condition>;

        e.g.
        =-> select*from product;
+----+----------+-----------+---------+
| id | pro_name | pro_price | pro_qty |
