|  1 | tv       |     20000 |      20 |
|  2 | Ac       |     65700 |      32 |
|  3 | Ac       |     32000 |      40 |
|  4 | Laptop   |     48000 |      60 |
|  5 | tv       |     35000 |      10 |
|  6 | phone    |     15000 |      30 |
+----+----------+-----------+---------+

